@startuml variant_a_seq_happy
title Вариант A - основной сценарий (push доставлен)

participant "Payment\nService" as PS
participant "Payment DB\n+ Outbox" as DB
participant "Outbox\nPoller" as OP
participant "Kafka" as K
participant "Delivery\nEngine" as DE
participant "Delivery DB" as DDB
participant "Push\nAdapter" as PA
participant "FCM" as FCM
participant "Пользователь" as U

PS -> DB : BEGIN TXN\nINSERT payment\nINSERT outbox(event)\nCOMMIT

OP -> DB : SELECT new outbox rows (polling / CDC)
DB --> OP : [notification_event]
OP -> K : Produce(txn.notifications, event)
OP -> DB : UPDATE outbox SET published = true

K --> DE : Consume(txn.notifications)
DE -> DDB : INSERT delivery(id, status=PENDING, idempotency_key)
DE -> DE : SELECT user preferences
DE -> PA : Send push(device_token, payload)
PA -> FCM : POST /fcm/send
FCM --> PA : 200 OK (message_id)
PA --> DE : accepted

note over DE : Ожидание receipt\n(таймаут 5 сек)

FCM -> U : Push notification
FCM -> DE : POST /webhook\n{ status: delivered, message_id }
DE -> DDB : UPDATE delivery SET status = DELIVERED

note over U : P99 <= 3 сек от события

@enduml
